# AeroWorks Operations Control Center — environment variables
#
# Phase 1 runs entirely on local mock data and requires no environment
# variables. This file is a placeholder for later phases (feature flags,
# environment-specific URLs). Never commit real values — copy this file
# to `.env.local` and fill values in locally.
#
# Example (unused in Phase 1):
# VITE_FEATURE_AI_TRIAGE=true
